divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking in the woods, and a green man walked up to me, and punched me in the face. He took me into his spaceship and probed me. I now feel very weird, and i can rotate my neck 360 degrees. I found a piece of its clothing outside of my home, too. I have it, its a shiny silver jacket with a weird alien design on it.
Summary: A shiny, silver saucer flying above my home
